<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(و. ا. ي)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">غيظ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>غِظْتُه، وأنا أغِيْظُه غَيْظاً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والتَّغَيُّظُ:</span> الاغْتِيَاظ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وبَنُو غَيْظٍ:</span> حَيٌّ من قَيْسٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وفلانٌ يُغايِظُ فلاناً:</span> إذا باراه فَصَنَعَ مِثْلَ صَنِيْعِه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>